OriginX GigShield - Team Documentation (Current Project Status)

1) Project Overview
- Goal: Parametric insurance for delivery partners affected by disruptions (rainfall, heat, AQI, curfews, etc.).
- Core idea: Automatic, trigger-based payouts with fraud controls and pricing logic.

2) Current Build Status
- Backend API: Implemented and test-covered for core pricing/fraud/disruption logic.
- Frontend: Kickoff starter added in `frontend/` for immediate UI work and API connectivity checks.
- AI scripts: Present in `ai/` for risk/anomaly experimentation.

3) Implemented Backend APIs
- `POST /api/delivery-partners/register`
- `GET /api/delivery-partners/:partnerId`
- `POST /api/insurance-policies/subscribe`
- `GET /api/insurance-policies/metadata/pricing-model`
- `GET /api/insurance-policies/:policyId`
- `POST /api/insurance-claims/submit`
- `GET /api/insurance-claims/:claimId`
- `GET /api/health`

